      "writtenOn": "2021-03-30T11:05:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This won\u0027t dedupe if the ScheduleBuild request is retried with a different batch containing the same requests, for example if the caller retries a subset of the builds handled in a previous request. Is that an issue for ResultDB? It would be nice if it could dedupe by individual requests in a batch.\n\nNot batching at all avoids this problem while simultaneously simplifying implementation, though the obvious trade-off is that it\u0027s inefficient.",
      "revId": "ae81b31b939260bb8b6d9983061b0f0fa1c4460e",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
