      "writtenOn": "2021-03-31T04:47:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e But if it\u0027s the partial retry where a batch contains a subset of already handled builds, I think the ResultDB won\u0027t dedup it and would create new invocations?\n\nResultDB will return error in this case: http://shortn/_JsDbWt26Pz\n\nAnd IIUC we tried to avoid this case by constructing the request id using the first build id in the batch and the length of the batch.",
      "parentUuid": "d94df4c3_db0279d6",
      "revId": "ae81b31b939260bb8b6d9983061b0f0fa1c4460e",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
